{"type": "article", "id": 26467, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-06T07:07:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27256, "name": "Q5"}, {"id": 27257, "name": "Backpack Chair"}, {"id": 27258, "name": "Trace collection"}, {"id": 27259, "name": "La Belle Époque"}, {"id": 27260, "name": "夜半のみどり"}, {"id": 7084, "name": "爆米花"}, {"id": 21167, "name": "抹茶"}, {"id": 23074, "name": "ODESD2"}, {"id": 27261, "name": "Bago Bago"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 27262, "name": "Larose Guyon"}, {"id": 27263, "name": "伊藤久右衛門"}, {"id": 27264, "name": "Diz-Diz"}, {"id": 27265, "name": "TATABI STUDIO"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162019ODsR46vC0eGcdTuU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Q5 by ODESD2</h2>\n<p class=\"\">还记得小时候玩过的折纸游戏吗？<a href=\"http://odesd2.com/\">ODESD2</a> 设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://odesd2.com/en/furniture/chairs/q5_chair\">Q5</a> 的椅子棱角分明，看上去像是一个被放大的折纸作品。实际上由铝合金制成的 Q5 不仅坚固也非常轻便，底座还有多种颜色可选。不仅如此，它座位上的毛毡也可以定制。售价为 326 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120726VyeWHGPKM5DScotj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120726bjBvHrCVZxKlft7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120727g4SpLEiwjRkdAPv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120727mkBiyYu1lEZvGQ65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207287WoXnlxA8grF4u9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120728GeQnyMhRvrIESsW7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h1 itemprop=\"name\">Backpack Chair by Bago Bago</h1>\n<p class=\"\">听说这个世界上有两种人：在哪儿都能坐下的人，以及（即便很累了）一直都站着的人。无论你是哪一种，Bago Bago 推出的这款能“变身”成椅子（当然有的时候你也可以放上其他东西，比如棋盘什么的）的背包都能满足你的需求，在你想休息却找不到椅子的时候将内置的折叠椅打开就行了。这个神奇的背包椅还提供了多种可选的颜色，售价为 137 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.ckie.com/products/backpack-chair-bago-bago\">链接</a>了解更详细的规格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120729d14ImqPrXya6Lti7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207299wAVilnM7buQ2HrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120729qMnyKQLofi1PEZH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120730xOrAeFjwBiK1nt6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120730fb8MhAPI6tCHTdpF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312073154LI1sejdaWzvbCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Trace collection by Nendo</h2>\n<p class=\"\">下面这几张图并不是什么视觉错觉，而是日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/tag/nendo\">Nendo</a> 制作的一个名为 Trace 的家具系列。就好像你不会在柜门前放上花瓶一样，Nendo 的设计师利用黑色金属线条将橱柜门开合的轨迹可视化，希望人们能重新审视空间、日常生活同家具间的联系。这个系列目前在纽约举办的 <a href=\"http://collectivedesignfair.com/\">Collective Design Fair</a> 上展出，展览将持续到 5 月 18 日。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120731ujVhWmblfq3Tg9Fs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207321LTlYDmO9g0BZIry.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207326VtS7b5KuL3TRpmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207324EpvWYibuRcHQse7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120733Q3ytPVC62DIvRx57.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120733NR1XIZfFAHtwdM9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>La Belle Époque by Larose Guyon</h2>\n<p class=\"\">如果给灯具“戴上”首饰，可能就是 <a href=\"http://www.laroseguyon.com/\">Larose Guyon</a> 新近推出的 La Belle Époque 雕塑灯具的模样。在 Audrée L. Larose 和 Félix Guyon 这对恋人设计师看来，灯具无关于风格，而是与光本身有关。系列中的三款灯具均由黄铜制成，造型简单优雅，衬托出灯光的温暖。这一系列将在 5 月 14 日至 5 月 17 日举行的纽约 ICFF 家具展上展出，你还可以通过<a href=\"http://www.laroseguyon.com/collections/\">链接</a>了解三款灯具的详细规格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120733QEg0xkFwpiK4CYqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207340F8zMl46woySuVvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120734Ag1rYlRuoXGVjpkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120735iNQ2LudwWTf3cP58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120735bahpm9XTiLunBCdG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120736h9m6cP0BHj82eSvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">夜半のみどり by 伊藤久右衛門</span></h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个绿色的葡萄酒其实是日本商家又一次脑洞大开的产物：京都抹茶品牌<a href=\"http://www.rakuten.ne.jp/gold/itohkyuemon/ujicha_t/\">伊藤久右衛門</a>和丹波葡萄酒合作推出了一款抹茶味葡萄酒，而且还取了一个特别直白的名字叫“夜半のみどり”（みどり是绿色的意思）。它的酒精度数仅为 12%，一口饮下能同时品尝到葡萄的酸甜和抹茶微涩的后味。300 毫升装的售价为 1200 日元，你可以通过日本的<a href=\"http://item.rakuten.co.jp/itohkyuemon/c/0000000489/\">樂天市場</a>购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120736LbZAWlj1pTgQ87aE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120736KMYTjhNOzVH8yZfW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120737zjGWpBydPFL7UnA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120737YlRQMxLZutmJnFpk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Diz-Diz Popcorn by TATABI STUDIO</span></h2>\n<p class=\"\">西班牙的 <a href=\"http://tatabistudio.com/\">TATABI Studio</a> 最近为 Diz-Diz 微波炉爆米花设计的包装选择了高端奢侈路线，颠覆了大众对这一零食的认识。干酪、咖喱、肉桂和香草四种口味以不同金属色的包装分装，外包装的纸盒则印刷上了大理石纹，折叠之后还能用来盛爆米花，既时尚又实用。对爆米花爱好者们而言，可能又带来了另一种（甜蜜的）烦恼：因为太好看即便买回家也舍不得吃。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<font face=\"Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, Microsoft YaHei, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial sans-serif\"></font><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207385d6Va0vo4JnmCzjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120738XjtnyMV7e6ALlx9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120739Sy92KWfb1RYvDVjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120739jedPRtYCFbqpVzf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120740knm4FltzCawrBgeQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120740cQ2vIoiBdJHS60XE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}